  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A batch of banana milkshakes consists of <math alttext=\"4\"><mn>4</mn>\n</math> cups of ice cream and <math alttext=\"2\"><mn>2</mn>\n</math> bananas and has <math alttext=\"1,114 milligrams left parenthesis mg right parenthesis\"><mn>1,114</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>milligrams</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mfenced><mtext>mg</mtext></mfenced></math> of calcium. There is <math alttext=\"276 mg\"><mn>276</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>mg</mtext></math> of calcium in <math alttext=\"1\"><mn>1</mn>\n</math> cup of the ice cream used to make this batch of milkshakes. How much calcium, <math alttext=\"in mg\"><mtext>in</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>mg</mtext></math>, is in <math alttext=\"1\"><mn>1</mn>\n</math> banana?</p>",
